[30;1m64 | [0m[35m          When set to an integer, the callback saves the checkpoint every[0m
[30;1m65 | [0m[35m          `save_freq` batches. Set `save_freq=False` only if using[0m
[30;1m66 | [0m[35m          preemption checkpointing (i.e. with `save_before_preemption=True`).[0m

[30;1m141 | [0m[35m    Rematerialization is a memory optimization technique that trades off[0m
[30;1m142 | [0m[35m    computation for memory. Instead of storing intermediate results[0m
[30;1m143 | [0m[35m    (e.g. activations) for backpropagation, they are recomputed during the[0m
[30;1m144 | [0m[35m    backward pass. This reduces peak memory usage at the cost of increased[0m

[30;1m115 | [0m[35m        # The indices of the data are shuffled and batched, and these indices[0m
[30;1m116 | [0m[35m        # are then zipped with the data and used to extract a batch of the data[0m
[30;1m117 | [0m[35m        # at each step. The performance improvements here come from:[0m
